@Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5129
@GroupId = 1
@CardId = 1

### Cards Health
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/cards/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Groups (userId = external user Guid from cards.users)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/cards/groups?userId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Accept: application/json

###

### Distinct front/back side-type pairs from user's groups (unordered: EN+PL == PL+EN; sorted as SideType1 <= SideType2)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/cards/side-type-pairs?userId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Accept: application/json

###

### Total word (card) count for user across all groups
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/cards/words-count?userId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Accept: application/json

###

### Cards due before tomorrow 00:00 UTC (includes overdue). Optional: questionSideType + answerSideType
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/cards/due-today-count?userId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Accept: application/json

###

### Due today — only groups with front EN + back PL
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/cards/due-today-count?userId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001&questionSideType=EN&answerSideType=PL
Accept: application/json

###

### Lesson words — karty z jednej grupy na dziś (UTC), kierunek musi zgadzać się z typami stron grupy (EN→PL albo PL→EN)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/cards/groups/{{GroupId}}/lesson-words?userId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001&questionSideType=EN&answerSideType=PL&limit=20
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Group
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/cards/groups
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "name": "English Basics",
  "frontSideType": "EN",
  "backSideType": "PL"
}

###

### Update Group
PATCH {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/cards/groups/{{GroupId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "name": "English Basics Updated",
  "frontSideType": "EN",
  "backSideType": "PL"
}

###

### Search cards — userId required; drawer / groupId optional; getCount & getList default false (at least one must be true)
### Pagination: page (default 1), pageSize (default 50, max 500) — applies to list; count is always total matching rows
### List only
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/cards/search?userId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001&drawer=2&groupId=1&getList=true&page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

###

### Count only (number of matching cards)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/cards/search?userId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001&drawer=2&getCount=true
Accept: application/json

###

### Count + list (JSON: { "count", "items" }) — items are one page
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/cards/search?userId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001&getCount=true&getList=true&page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

###

### Add Card To Group
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/cards/cards
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "groupId": 1,
  "frontLabel": "apple",
  "backLabel": "jablko",
  "frontExample": "I eat an apple.",
  "frontComment": "fruit",
  "backExample": "Jem jablko.",
  "backComment": "owoc"
}

###

### Update Card
PATCH {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/cards/{{CardId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "front": {
    "label": "pear",
    "example": "I eat a pear.",
    "comment": "fruit"
  },
  "back": {
    "label": "gruszka",
    "example": "Jem gruszke.",
    "comment": "owoc"
  }
}

###

### Tick SRS result (sets is_ticked = true). resultId = cards.results.id
PUT {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/cards/tick
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "resultId": 1
}
